{"tid":1385072,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[超合作運動] 熱烈表達對施政報告嘅意見","createTime":"2019-07-30T03:57:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T04:00:16.000Z","uid":148983,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"12caed05528ce7f7224d216f730195c8e8576260","tid":1385072,"uid":148983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:57:27.000Z","msg":"原來班過街老鼠靜靜雞開始咗2019施政報告諮詢<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>作爲關心政府施政嘅香港市民<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span><br />\n就當然要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">踴躍發表意見啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">《施政報告》諮詢工作展開<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n  特區政府今日（七月十日）就二○一九年《施政報告》展開公眾諮詢。行政長官林鄭月娥、政務司司長張建宗和財政司司長陳茂波會陸續與不同界別人士會面，聽取他們的意見。<br />\n<br />\n  林鄭月娥說：「要持續發展經濟，改善民生，需要我們一起籌謀，同心協力。我誠邀各位市民就《施政報告》發表意見，讓我們可以集思廣益，制訂切合市民需要的政策措施。我和我的團隊會虛心聆聽廣大市民的聲音，並在我的第三份《施政報告》中作出回應。」</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">市民可登入網站（<a href=\"http://www.policyaddress.gov.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.policyaddress.gov.hk&d=BNsYvnDu2JTLJ%2Bl7stKmI8F4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=bdf858f1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.policyaddress.gov.hk</a>）、在二○一九年《施政報告》公眾諮詢的Facebook專頁（<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/PolicyAddress2019）或Instagram（www.instagram.com/policyaddress2019）留言，亦可透過電郵（policyaddress@pico.gov.hk）、電話（2432\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FPolicyAddress2019%EF%BC%89%E6%88%96Instagram%EF%BC%88www.instagram.com%2Fpolicyaddress2019%EF%BC%89%E7%95%99%E8%A8%80%EF%BC%8C%E4%BA%A6%E5%8F%AF%E9%80%8F%E9%81%8E%E9%9B%BB%E9%83%B5%EF%BC%88policyaddress%40pico.gov.hk%EF%BC%89%E3%80%81%E9%9B%BB%E8%A9%B1%EF%BC%882432&d=BNsYvnDu2JTLJ%2Bl7stKmI8F4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=e8fbb79c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.facebook.com/PolicyAddress2019）或Instagram（www.instagram.com/policyaddress2019）留言，亦可透過電郵（policyaddress@pico.gov.hk）、電話（2432</a> 1899）或傳真（2537 9083）就《施政報告》提交意見。</span></strong></span><br />\n <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">完<br />\n2019年7月10日（星期三）<br />\n香港時間16時15分</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Source: <a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201907/10/P2019071000594.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201907%2F10%2FP2019071000594.htm&d=BNsYvnDu2JTLJ%2Bl7stKmI8F4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=cb7e9366\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201907/10/P2019071000594.htm</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></strong></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />8.5全民罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span></div>"},{"pid":"ec3ec2920afa9073ad7a03d14d28823fb0496419","tid":1385072,"uid":148983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:58:10.000Z","msg":"自推十次 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<code>8.5 全民罷工</code>"},{"pid":"35ca9e9ac965d2a042dde8b51e6e3c9d8ebb2fce","tid":1385072,"uid":148983,"like":0,"dislike":0